{
  "texts": [
    "See supplementary methods for the templates used.",
    "The three scoring criteria were:• Biological accuracy: is the textual definition biologically accurate?",
    "• Internal consistency: is the structure and content of the definition consistent with other definitions in the ontology, and with the style guide for that ontology?",
    "• Overall score: overall utility of the definition.For each of these metrics, an ordinal scale of 1-5 was used, with 1 being the worst, 3 being acceptable, and 5 being the best.",
    "Assigning a consistency score was optional."
  ]
}